data.title: Marines TV
data.meta_description: Recruits with Lima Company, 3rd Recruit Training Battalion, participate in the confidence course during a training event at Marine Corps Recruit Depot, San Diego, California, March 9, 2021. The confidence course is designed to give recruits the opportunity to challenge themselves and gain the confidence to overcome obstacles. (U.S. Marine Corps video by Cpl. Ana S. Madrigal)
